Contributing
Issues and pull requests welcome.
What's useful
Sector-specific annexes (healthcare, HR, finance, public sector)
Additional language versions
Updates as AI Act delegated acts and CNIL guidance are published
Anonymised real-world test cases showing how the template was applied
Guidelines
Keep the template practical. Every question should have a concrete answer in a real project.
Do not add questions that duplicate GDPR Art. 35 obligations that are already covered.
Regulatory references must cite the exact article. Do not paraphrase obligations.
French and English versions must stay in sync.
Opening an issue
Use issues to report gaps, outdated references, or structural problems.
Describe the specific section and the regulatory basis for the proposed change.
Pull requests
Small, focused PRs are easiest to review. One logical change per PR.
